_lc_thickness_1.value: Expected layer height after first layer deposition

_lc_thickness_2.value: Expected layer height after second layer deposition

_lc_thickness_3.value: Expected layer height after third layer deposition

_lc_thickness_other.value: Expected layer height for each subsequent layer deposition

_wall_offset.value: Distance from wall to be rejected by centerline segment

_wall_appendix.value: Branch termination distance of the centerline segment

offsetCount.value: Creates additional contour paths around the raster paths

ToolVec_i.value: Component I of the tool vector

ToolVec_j.value: Component J of the tool vector

ToolVec_k.value: Component K of the tool vector

OrientVec_offset_angle.value: Offsets the given vector orientation by this offset angle

point_reduction.value: Reduce number of points on a curve
